title: Proxyon - Discography (1989-2005) [MP3 at 320Kbps]
description:
Proxyon is a very interesting synthdance project founded by Michiel van der Kuy (Laserdance, Koto, Rygar). First two Proxyon records were co-produced by Michiel van der Kuy and Rob van Eijk. Third album, "Return Of Tarah" has a little different sound, because it was made by a different (and mysterious) producer who called himself "Jay Vee".

Proxyon is a classic synthdance act, the music has very cosmic feeling and the songs are arranged in famous Michiel van der Kuy's style (except for "Return of Tarah" which contains also synthdance music, but arranged in a different style).
